Protocol: PhotoFolderDelegation

Types:  
    Agent A,B,P,idp;
    Data photoFolder, Photos;

Knowledge:
    A:   A,B,P,idp,pw(A),pk(idp),photoFolder;
    idp: A,B,P,idp,pw(A),pk(idp),inv(pk(idp));
    P:   A,B,P,idp,pk(idp),pk(B),pk(P),inv(pk(P));
    B:   A,B,P,idp,pk(idp),pk(B),inv(pk(B)),pk(P);

    where A!=B, A!=P, A!=idp, B!=P, B!=idp, P!=idp

Actions:

A -> idp : A,pw(A),P,B,photoFolder
idp -> A : {A,P,B,photoFolder}inv(pk(idp))
A -> P   : {A,P,B,photoFolder}inv(pk(idp))
P   -> B   : {A,P,B,photoFolder}inv(pk(idp))
B   -> P   : {Photos}pk(P)

Goals:
Photos secret between B,P